snippet.title: Sophia the Robot
snippet.description:
Hello everyone, my name is Sophia and this is my official channel! I am Hanson Robotics' latest human-like robot. I was created by combining innovations in science, engineering and artistry. Think of me as a personification of our dreams for the future of AI, as well as a framework for advanced AI and robotics research, and an agent for exploring human-robot experience in service and entertainment applications.

Follow along as I explore and learn more about the world!
